Feature: DailyLedger

Background:
	Given User log into Dispute Tracking Application
	And User should be able to see Dashboard in Application

@DailyLedger
Scenario: Daily Ledger
	 Given User clicks the Ledger Icon on the Dashboard Page
	And User clicks the Daily Ledger Icon from the dropdown of Ledger
	And User validates the following fields on the Daily Ledger Page
		| Fields         |
		| Refresh Ledger |
		| Date           |
		| Account        |
		| Customer       |
		| Amount         |
		| Type           |
		| Tran Code      |
		| Description    |
	And User clicks the Dashboard Icon